Class SpectrumIdentification

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, MassSpecObject

    public class SpectrumIdentification
extends IdentifiableParamGroup
    PSM Spectrum identification match. The relation between an Spectrum and a PeptideEvidence. It contains a number of Scores from different search Engines.
